              <p align="center"><font size="2" face="Arial" color="#000080"><b>Promotion
              Ceremony</b></font></p>
              <p><font size="2" face="Arial">After the Duke/Duchess has
              officially sanctions the promotion of a person, the following
              ceremony, including oath, is performed. The officer presiding over
              the promotion ceremony reads the following:<br>
              <br>
              1) &lt;Person(s) being promoted&gt;, as you have heard,
              Duke/Duchess &lt;name&gt; of &lt;duchy&gt; has approved your
              promotion to the rank of &lt;rank&gt;, will you accept the
              position? aye or nay.&nbsp;<br>
              <br>
              2) Very well, please step forward and kneel before me. (After the
              person(s) step(s) forward and kneel(s). The officer draws his/her
              sword of promotion and holds it in a salute position).<br>
              <br>
              3) &lt;name(s)&gt;, do you promise to continue to abide by the
              charter of *NOR/ in carrying out your duties as a &lt;rank&gt; of
              &lt;duchy&gt;?<br>
              <br>
              4) Do you promise to continue to conform to the Standards and
              Conventions &amp; Jacket Creed of the Guild of *NOR/ as a
              &lt;rank&gt; of &lt;duchy&gt;?<br>
              <br>
              5) Do you promise to carry out the duties of a &lt;rank&gt; (if
              officer) [as presented in the &lt;rank&gt; mandate]?<br>
              <br>
              6) Do you promise to show restraint in using your powers,
              remembering to contact your superior officer before taking drastic
              actions?<br>
              <br>
              7) Very well, then by the power vested in me by Duke/Duchess
              &lt;name&gt; of &lt;duchy&gt;, I hereby promote you to the Rank of
              &lt;rank&gt; of the Guild of *NOR/. Congratulations!!!&nbsp;<br>
              <br>
              8) &lt;officer sheaths sword&gt;<br>
              <br>
              After the ceremony, Notify the Duchy/Branch Leader &amp; Herald of
              the promotion. MAKE SURE THE PERSONS E-MAIL ADDRESS IS CORRECT.</font></p>
